series: Revue des Nouvelles Technologies de l'Information
title: Fabrique logicielle de réseaux sociaux spécialisés (aspects fonctionnels)
abstract: This paper introduces a software factory for developing social networks. This factory takesan abstract social network and creates a concrete one, using mechanisms such as sub-typingand behavior overloading.
authors: Benjamin Billet, David Fernandez, Didier Parigot
